  <div class="space-y-24">
    <!-- Feature Row 1: Embedded Systems -->
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-10 mb-24">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h2>Embedded Systems</h2>
        <p>Mind brings modern language features to bare-metal development, making embedded programming safer and more productive.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Memory Safety without GC:</strong> Prevent buffer overflows and null pointer dereferences at compile time.</li>
          <li><strong>Hardware Abstraction:</strong> Write reusable drivers with zero runtime overhead using Mind's powerful type system.</li>
          <li><strong>Cross-Compilation:</strong> First-class support for ARM, RISC-V, and AVR architectures out of the box.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative w-full h-[250px] md:h-[350px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-slate-200 bg-[#E6E9F2]" id="embedded-slideshow-container">
          <img src="/img/features/case_frame1.jpeg" id="slide-0" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-1000 block scale-[1.02]" style="opacity: 1;" />
          <img src="/img/features/case_frame2.jpeg" id="slide-1" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-1000 block scale-[1.02]" style="opacity: 0;" />
          <img src="/img/features/case_frame3.jpeg" id="slide-2" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-1000 block scale-[1.02]" style="opacity: 0;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Row 2: Cloud Infrastructure -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 mb-24">
